{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"opacity","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/opacity","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p>opacity 属性指定了一个对象或一组对象的透明度，也就是说，元素后面的背景的透过率。</p>\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性，请阅读 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/opacity\"><code>css opacity</code></a>以了解更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th>外观属性</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td>&lt;opacity-value&gt; | inherit</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可变性</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"opacity-value\">&lt;opacity-value&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一致的不透明度设置，作为一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a>被应用到整个对象上。任何超过范围 0.0 到 1.0 的值都会被压回这个范围。0.0 表示完全透明，1.0 表示完全不透明。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>opacity</code>属性：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#graphics\">图形元素</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/defs\"><code>&lt;defs&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#transparency","title":"CSS Color Module Level 4"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/render.html#ObjectAndGroupOpacityProperties","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.opacity"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/opacity\"><code>css opacity</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"opacity","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/opacity","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/opacity/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG：可缩放矢量图形"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/opacity","title":"opacity"}],"pageTitle":"opacity - SVG：可缩放矢量图形 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}